TVS Racing is doing a fabulous job in enabling and promoting motorcycle racing through their academy. They have made the process of joining the world of motorsports so easy and accessible that what one needs is just the passion to be a motorcycle racer. Everything else is enabled and taken care of by TVS Racing thru a well established rider development program. Not just that, TVS was the first Indian manufacturer to set up a racing academy decades ago. Watch this video till the end to understand how you can also join the TVS Racing program. This video was shot during the INMRC finale and it was quite a spectacle. Find out all about the star riders and their achievements during the INMRC season, not to forget how amazing the TVS Apache RR310 and RTR160 bikes are 💙🏁❤️

At Car Girls India 🇮🇳 our goal is to always bring to you high quality automotive entertainment in the form of films and content that we produce globally and all over India. Having worked with the crème de la crème of the automotive brands, OEMs in India, USA, all over Europe and the Middle East, while grateful, we also understand that our journey is still in its infancy and our promise to you is to strive harder to make our productions, films and content even better.
.
We learn with you, we make mistakes, we learn again and that’s always how it will be. Car Girls India 🇮🇳 will continue bringing to you all stylish, exclusive and informative automotive entertainment in our own unapologetic way. None of this would have been possible without the support of you lovely fans and followers, a huge huge HEARTFELT THANK YOU 💙🙏
.
Thank You @cosmoindia and @royalenfield for recognizing our work and inspiring us to do even better in the future 🙏🤗💙

Fastag or Slow Tag? The wait times at some toll booths especially on long weekends has become a nightmare. Also despite assured waivers of Fastag toll fee if one has to wait beyond a stipulated time, no one is given that waiver. Huge pile up of vehicles at Fastag booths mean more often than not ambulances and other emergency vehicles are stuck in this chaos, something has to be done about this issue soon.
.
@cargirlsindia motoring show 🇮🇳
.

What makes Fernando Alonso a bonafide motorsports GOAT 🐐also known as ‘El Padre’, he is more than just a Formula One great - he is a true motorsports legend. Alonso is a two-time Formula One champion, World Endurance Champion, two-time Le Mans 24-hour winner, Daytona 24-hour winner, and karting world champion. He almost achieved the prestigious ‘triple crown’ of motorsports by winning the Le Mans, Monaco Grand Prix, and Indy 500; not just that an epic Dakar debut too, he didn’t even spare the World Rally Raid scene. These are things Drive to Survive or DTS hardly ever talks about.
.
Dear Fernando @fernandoalo_oficial lots of love from your fans in India 💙
.
@cargirlsindia motoring show 🇮🇳
.

Understanding different types of motor vehicle  insurance will ensure you make the right choice and don’t feel cheated during a claim. Third party insurance only covers damages caused to others, while comprehensive insurance also protects your own vehicle. The key difference is that zero depreciation cover reimburses the full repair cost, without deducting for depreciation.
.
